General.Name: Plenti Group Ltd
General.Description: Plenti Group Limited engages in the fintech lending business in Australia. The company offers personal, car, wedding, legal fee, motorcycle, and dental loans; green, holiday, debt consolidation, and EV loans, as well as engages in auto refinancing activities. It also offers automotive and renewable energy related loans. Plenti Group Limited was founded in 2014 and is headquartered in Sydney, Australia.
